snippet.title: Amber Rose Seems to Regret Getting Drunk and Telling the World That Kanye West Doesn't Write His Own
snippet.description:
Is Amber Rose finally done with the Kanye West comments?
She appears to have seen the error of her ways this morning, posting on Instagram a shot of Steve Carell as gaffe-spewing Michael Scott on The Office. Rose, who was once engaged to the rapper, was caught on video at L.A.'s Supper Club earlier this week ranting that West didn't write his own music after, apparently, the DJ put on a Kanye tune.
